#: ../../source/tools.rst:91
msgid ""
"The RTRlib implements the client-side of the RPKI-RTR protocol "
"(:RFC:`6810`, :RFC:`8210`) and BGP Prefix Origin Validation "
"(:RFC:`6811`). This also enables the maintenance of router keys, which "
"are required to deploy BGPSec."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tools.rst:96
msgid ""
"RTRlib was originally founded by researchers from the Computer Systems & "
"Telematics group at Freie Universität Berlin and reseachers from the INET"
" research group at Hamburg University of Applied Sciences, under the "
"supervision of Matthias Wählisch and Thomas Schmidt. It is now a "
"community project."
msgstr ""

